<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فِي الْأَظْهر<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَمُقَابِله الْمَنْع<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَتَصِح<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>لوَارث فِي الْأَظْهر إِن جَازَ بَاقِي الْوَرَثَة<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>المطلقين التَّصَرُّف وَمُقَابل الْأَظْهر بُطْلَانهَا وَإِن أَجَازُوا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَلَا عِبْرَة بردهمْ وإجازتهم فِي حَيَاة الْمُوصى وَالْعبْرَة فِي كَونه<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
